title: Prior Labs - Gold Sponsor of PyCon DE & PyData
---
full_description: Prior Labs is building breakthrough foundation models that understand spreadsheets and databases - the lifeblood of science and business. While foundation models have transformed text and images, tabular data has remained largely untouched. Prior Labs is tackling this opportunity to revolutionize how the world approaches scientific discovery, medical research, financial modeling, and business intelligence. Its model TabPFN, published in Nature, sets a new state-of-the-art for tabular machine learning and has reached 3M downloads and 6,000 GitHub stars, with adoption across Fortune 500 companies and data science teams worldwide. Founded in 2024 and based in Freiburg, Berlin, and New York, Prior Labs is led by Frank Hutter, Noah Hollmann, and Sauraj Gambhir, backed by Balderton Capital, and advised by Yann LeCun and Bernhard Schölkopf. Learn more at priorlabs.ai.

